WEBVTT

00:02.888 --> 00:06.207
You are being watched.

00:06.209 --> 00:07.592
The government
has a secret system--

00:07.594 --> 00:12.247
A machine that spies on you
every hour of every day.

00:12.249 --> 00:14.465
I know, because I built it.

00:14.467 --> 00:16.901
I designed the machine
to detect acts of terror,

00:16.903 --> 00:18.670
but it sees everything...

00:18.672 --> 00:21.455
Violent crimes
involving ordinary people,

00:21.457 --> 00:22.891
people like you,

00:22.893 --> 00:26.561
crimes the government
considered irrelevant.

00:26.563 --> 00:29.931
They wouldn't act,
so I decided I would.

00:29.933 --> 00:31.799
But I needed a partner--

00:31.801 --> 00:34.485
Someone with the skills
to intervene.

00:34.487 --> 00:38.690
Hunted by the authorities,
we work in secret.

00:38.692 --> 00:40.641
You will never find us.

00:40.643 --> 00:42.643
But victim or perpetrator,

00:42.645 --> 00:46.030
if your number's up,
we'll find you.

00:46.666 --> 00:50.743
